Text: The patch needs to be changed on the same day every week. If you forgot, you need to change it ASAP and figure out how late you are. If you’re more than two days late changing it, use condoms if you have have sex for the next week. Keep that new patch on for a week, and maybe set a reminder so you don’t forget to change it next week!
